# Medusa-backend-server-setup-in local

# 

# 

# 

# 

# 

# **Overview**

● 	Installation of  dependencies

● 	creation of medusa server

● 	verification of server 

# 

# **Prerequisites**

* Node js   
* Postgres   
* Git     
* Medusa-cli 

# **Steps to server setup**

* To Verification of the node js server installation please execute the below command in the cmd 

           ** node \-v \<it will gives the nodejs server version\>**  
           ![][image2]

* If it is not installed means refer this link(make sure you choose installation method based on your os  ) → [node js installer](https://nodejs.org/en/download/prebuilt-installer)   
* To Verification of the postgres server installation please execute the below command in the cmd 

           ** Psql \-p \<psql port\> \-U postgres \<it want prompt for password if it is installed\>**  
**![][image3]**

* If it is not installed means refer this link(make sure you choose installation method based on your os  ) → [postgres\_installer](https://www.postgresql.org/download/)  
* To Verification of the git server installation please execute the below command in the cmd  
  **git  \-v \<it will show the version of git installed \>**  
  ![][image4]  
* If it is not installed means refer this link(make sure you choose installation method based on your os  ) →  [git\_instaler](https://git-scm.com/download/win)   
* After that we need install the medusa cli by using by below command 

           **npm install @medusajs/medusa-cli \-g**

* Verify the installation by using **medusa \-v**  
  **![][image5]**  
* Please refer  this link if you faced any error regarding the medusa cli **→ [medusa-cli-issue](https://docs.medusajs.com/development/backend/prepare-environment#troubleshooting-installation)**  
* After successful installation of the medusa cli we need create the server by using the below command 

          **medusa new \<project-name\>**  
       ** ![][image6]**

* **If you face any issue in while installing project regarding db or something please refer below link → [project creation issue](https://docs.medusajs.com/troubleshooting/create-medusa-app-errors)**  
* After installation of project please server the server by using **npx medusa develop** or **medusa develop**   
* Verify the admin portal and api port
